            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Maurus">Mauro</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName> offre pro
                        anima sua alla <rs key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di
                            <orgName key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/272">Santa
                            Maria que dicitur Foreporta</orgName>, alla <rs
                                key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di <orgName
                                    key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/292">San Michele
                            Arcangelo que dicitur af Fuore</orgName>, alla <rs
                            key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di <orgName
                                key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/242">San Pietro que
                            dicitur Maiore</orgName>, alla <rs key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e
                                canonica</rs> dei <orgName key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" 
                            ref="#juridical_persons/256">Santi Reparata e Pantaleone</orgName> posta
                        infra <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities">Lucensi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> prope il <rs key="#Mother_churches"
                            >vescovato</rs> di <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/69"
                            key="#Mother_churches">San Martino</orgName>, alla <rs
                            key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di <orgName
                                key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/294">San
                            Donato</orgName> posta foris prope Lucense civitatem, alla <rs
                            key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di <orgName
                                key="#Collegiate_churches #Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/70">San
                            Frediano</orgName> posta prope <placeName ref="#places/4">Burgo qui
                            dicitur suprascripti Sancti Fridiani</placeName>, un appezzamento di
                        terra, quod est vinea et oliveto, posto in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/633">Scleto ubi dicitur alle Quarre</placeName> et prope la
                            <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3112" key="#Churches">San Giovanni</orgName>,
                            <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> uno capo in via
                        publica, alio capo con terra del <rs key="#Judge">giudice</rs>
                                <persName key="#Judge #Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Sigefredus">Sighifridi</name></persName>, lato uno con
                                terra della <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches">Santa Reparata</orgName>, alio lato
                                con terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName> et
                        de suis consortibus, per una misura complessiva di 6 staia et dimidium con
                        tutte le sue dipendenze. Chiede al <rs key="#Notary #Writer">notaio imperiale</rs>
                                <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName> la stesura
                        della cartula. Actum Luca. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori:
                                <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                    <name ref="Brunus">Bruno</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Tassus">Tasso</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                    ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>, gg. <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                        ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName> e <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                    <name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Villanus">Villano</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Carbo">Carbone</name></persName>. </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
